---
title: Beefy Taco Casserole with Mixed Green Salad
description: Ever had a night where you just couldn’t decide what to have for dinner because there are just so many delicious things to make? This recipe is for you. We’re marrying two of our favorites—tacos and lasagna—to create a casserole that features lively Tex-Mex flavors in bubbly, baked form. As you savor the layers of meaty filling, tortillas, and cheese piled high, you’ll wonder why there aren’t more dishes that capture the best of both worlds so perfectly.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/taco-casserole-cbf3f8ff.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/taco-casserole-c29d5c21.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
